title: Pts JanuStore Prestashop Themes
description:
Pts Janus is a Responsive Prestashop Theme for multi-purposes with modern style: Fashion, Furniture, Cosmetics or even a Hitech store, the demo says it all. Pts Janus is built with the best Prestashop Drag and Drop Page Builder, its own theme control panel includes a lots of options to manage and customize your store.

The endless possibilities Prestashop theme integrates over 50 Prestashop widgets that will be very useful to build content for your store, just assign widget to any position in the layout you want. It also supports multiple Prestashop modules to implement special features in the theme like slideshow, quick view, etc. Pts Janus is optimized by compressing CSS & JS, clean and well coding structure.

Pts Janus is ease of customization theme with Live Theme Editor, the truly magic tool will help you customize your store with pre-defined parameters. Pts Janus theme core is powered with new web technologies: Bootstrap 3, Font Awesome 4, SASS, HTML5 and CSS3
